97
00:05:10.720 --> 00:05:14.156
Being vulnerable and listening to others.
he just kept going.

98
00:05:14.240 --> 00:05:15.229
Rebbie Jackson
MICHAEL'S SISTER

99
00:05:15.680 --> 00:05:19.275
