103
00:05:33.200 --> 00:05:37.432
Steve would probably disagree with that.
but I felt

104
00:05:37.560 --> 00:05:39.516
you just went a bit too far.

105
00:05:42.080 --> 00:05:43.911
The disease that Michael had. vitiligo.

106
00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:44.989
Katherine Jackson
MICHAEL'S MOTHER

107
00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:47.276
Michael suffered from it and he...

108
00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:51.636
He didn't wanna be spotted up and he...

109
