1125
01:06:52.000 --> 01:06:54.355
And I'll always love him. always.

1126
01:06:56.560 --> 01:06:58.630
REBBIE: He was one of the warmest

1127
01:06:58.720 --> 01:07:02.110
and most loveable persons
